Liege Grenade Attack Kills Two, Leaves 47 Injured, Belgium’s RTBF Reports

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-12-13T13:55:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/liege-grenade-attack-kills-two-leaves-47-injured-belgium-s-rtbf-reports.html
An attack in the Belgian city of
Liege left at least two people dead and 47 injured, seven of
them gravely, RTBF television reported, citing the city
prosecutor’s office.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jim Brunsden in Brussels at 
